Review: Amazing cocktails and great happy hour prices for the city. We also got two appetizers and they were really filling. Highly recommend, they have happy hour until 7 PM!
Incredible Poboys. So many options and flavors. They have different twists on this Louisiana classic with Thai and other regional flavors. A number of vegetarian options as well.
Up Thai has always been good. Their Thai iced tea is stellar. This time some of the dishes were a bit bland while some were up to par. Beautiful decor.

We got the pesto linguine, buttermilk mashed potatoes, and Honeychild cocktail.
